data.description: Adorable single story 3 bedroom home on a double lot with mature oak trees. Recently renovated in 2021, this home has so much to offer! Roof, HVAC, flooring, majority of plumbing, fixtures and kitchen were all new at the time of remodel. Carpets were professionally cleaned upon seller move out. Yards from the Doodle Park & minutes from downtown Easley, this home is ideal for an active lifestyle. You will enjoy stainless steel appliances, two patios, a fenced in yard, carport, and large basement/crawlspace. Schedule a showing today!
